Package: gcammaptools
Title: Plot GCAM Output on Maps
Version: 0.0.2
Authors@R: c(
	   person("Catherine", "Ledna", email = "catherine.ledna@pnnl.gov", role = c("aut", "cre")),
	   person("Robert", "Link", email="robert.link@pnnl.gov", role="ctb")
	   )
Description: This package provides tools for displaying GCAM output plotted as shaded regions on
    maps (a type of plot called a "choropleth").  Both numerical and categorical data are supported.
    The package also provides a house style for GCAM maps, including color sets, projections, and
    theme elements.
Depends: R (>= 3.1.3)
License: GPL-2
LazyData: true
Imports: dplyr,
    ggplot2,
    ggalt (>=0.3.1.9000),
    graticule (>=0.1.2),
    mapproj,
    maptools,
    RColorBrewer,
    rgdal,	
    rgeos,
    sp
